# Git commits

Never add to commits, PRs, or commit messages:

- `Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>`
- `Made-with: Cursor` or any Cursor attribution trailer

When creating commits:

- Use only the user's name and email as author
- Keep commit messages clean — no AI/agent attribution lines
- If a hook or tool adds Cursor attribution, amend or rewrite the message before push

This repo uses `.githooks/prepare-commit-msg` to strip Cursor lines automatically. After clone, run once:

```bash
git config core.hooksPath .githooks
```
